Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.33,0:00:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄之军团？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.33,0:00:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(440,430)}<Legion>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.57,0:00:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄之王…为何在此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.71,0:00:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王…那么说他就是统帅黄之军团
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.71,0:00:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(593,430)}<Legion>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.86,0:00:24.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等级9的超频连接者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.86,0:00:24.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(470,430)}<Buster Linker>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.03,0:00:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.48,0:00:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都是你设计好的啊 黄之声波
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.48,0:00:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(567,430)}<Yellow Radio>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.29,0:00:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀 难道是还要和你说日安么 红之王
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.92,0:00:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是奇遇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.93,0:00:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你假惺惺啥啊 明摆着是在埋伏我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.96,0:00:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 绝对没错
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.02,0:00:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现实的1秒是这里的17分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.65,0:00:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是故意的 根本不可能在这里见面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.18,0:00:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说的那么过分
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.91,0:00:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想要让违反互不侵犯条约
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.80,0:00:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,袭击了我可爱的部下并迫使其损失全部的点数的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.88,0:01:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤之军团的某一位负起责任
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.88,0:01:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(342,430)}<Legion>
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.58,0:01:02.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而来到此地的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.06,0:01:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是他偷藏了「灾祸之铠」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.78,0:01:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后交给樱红之车
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.78,0:01:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(480,430)}<Cherry Rook>
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.87,0:01:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了引出仁子 腥红之雨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.87,0:01:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(512,430)}<Scarlet Rain>
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.03,0:01:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在互不侵犯条约写着有这么一条
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.93,0:01:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军团的成员因为违反条约遭受到攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.93,0:01:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(230,430)}<Legion>
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.41,0:01:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并被迫强制卸载「Brain Burst」的情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.03,0:01:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个军团可以从袭击方的军团中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.03,0:01:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(314,430)}<Legion>
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.03,0:01:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(565,430)}<Legion>
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.26,0:01:36.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选出任何一个人并让其遭受同样的困境
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.64,0:01:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到那个任何一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.20,0:01:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然就是红之军团的当主腥红之雨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.20,0:01:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(411,430)}<Legion>
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.20,0:01:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(577,430)}<Scarlet Rain>
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.32,0:01:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一切明摆的就只是为了能使自己达到等级10的必须的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.81,0:01:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五个首级其中之一啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.73,0:03:27.69,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\pos(662,393)}Obligation ; 宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.90,0:03:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}这样啊 是这个目的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.02,0:03:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}您能理解那是最好的了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.85,0:03:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是条约上也写了这么一句话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.13,0:03:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说可以选随机的一名进行复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.84,0:03:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但军团当主自己裁决违反者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.82,0:03:37.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(314,430)}<Legion>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.55,0:03:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将其点数全数剥夺的情况下就可以不作追究
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.14,0:03:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确 但我也听到了一些传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.01,0:03:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您似乎就已经尝试过了 不过却完败了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.02,0:03:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要再挑战的话 那是你的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.39,0:03:55.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那个家伙到底下次什么时候出现
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.16,0:03:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候可以打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.43,0:03:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不能现在马上就解决他的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.36,0:04:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来就只能用你来当沙包了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.71,0:04:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是个陷阱 仁子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.31,0:04:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们先暂时下线吧 然后等下次机会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.41,0:04:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.83,0:04:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这无限制中立舞台中是没办法随时下线的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.89,0:04:16.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的 小春
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.91,0:04:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要从这里离开的话 只能到各地设置的退出点才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.64,0:04:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系统就是这样设定的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.56,0:04:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话我们就先去退出点…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.95,0:04:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离这里最近的退出点是池袋和阳光都市
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.07,0:04:33.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么样 看来都要打上个一次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.79,0:04:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是呐 声波那个混帐也有误算
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.80,0:04:37.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(358,430)}<Radio>
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.57,0:04:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,误算？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.70,0:04:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 虽说那个混账为了我一个人聚集起了那么一帮人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.75,0:04:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们这里还有另外一个王
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.80,0:04:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这么回事 黑之睡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.78,0:04:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(510,430)}<Black Lotus>
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.47,0:04:56.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于接下来将要发生的嘉年华盛宴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:05:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您能在旁静静的观赏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.60,0:05:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑 黄之声波
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.58,0:05:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(498,430)}<Yellow Radio>
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.59,0:05:07.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问什么我要听从你的话按你的意图行事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.31,0:05:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 真是个不懂事的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,0:05:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏我还给你准备了这样的一份大礼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.48,0:05:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.33,0:05:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前代的王 红之骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.31,0:05:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(484,430)}<Red Rider>
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.70,0:05:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前代的王…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.70,0:05:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们战斗至今就是为了这么个无聊的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.84,0:05:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互相憎恶 互相掠夺 互相残杀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.92,0:05:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.80,0:05:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们统领各自的军团战斗至今
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.79,0:05:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(467,430)}<Legion>
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.49,0:05:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不是因为我们是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.33,0:05:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是因为我们是竞争对手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.35,0:05:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你的战斗方式啊 睡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.34,0:05:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(567,430)}<Lotus>
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.59,0:05:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有机会在现实生活中见面的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.36,0:05:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你肯定能成为朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.42,0:06:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…是想和你成为死党
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.50,0:06:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不想和以命相搏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.80,0:06:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也是这么想的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.33,0:06:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下 骑士 刚才那些话我们可不能听了就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.31,0:06:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(243,430)}<Rider>
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.69,0:06:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对啦 才不是那种意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.82,0:06:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是伤脑筋啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.75,0:06:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 就像你说的一样 骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.73,0:06:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(556,430)}<Rider>
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.53,0:06:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也挺喜欢你的 当然只是尊敬的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.09,0:06:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就知道你能懂我 睡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.08,0:06:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(526,430)}<Lotus>
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.02,0:06:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这真是抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.98,0:06:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么这么办吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.93,0:06:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.94,0:06:37.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下 等下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.57,0:06:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别生气 这只是握手的代替形式嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.59,0:06:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宣告·拥抱致死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.59,0:06:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(424,430)}<Death By Embracing>
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.92,0:07:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手…住手…住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.39,0:07:17.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.09,0:07:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春雪君…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.92,0:07:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐 学姐 学姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.93,0:07:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零化现象
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.92,0:07:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(424,430)}<Zero Field>
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.83,0:07:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡莲Louts 你竟然如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.55,0:07:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就知道你还是不能摆脱那次的背叛的阴影
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.19,0:07:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是还真没想到你靠那点觉悟目标等级10
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.62,0:07:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是笑得我肚子疼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.14,0:07:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击准备！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.65,0:07:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 强化外…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.76,0:07:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以 红之王
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.74,0:08:00.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一旦强化武装 就会失去机动力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.91,0:08:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在应该先撤退到阳光城市的退出点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.41,0:08:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春 我来挡一会儿 你快带着主人走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.62,0:08:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那样的话 你就…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们在打倒红之王后 一定会盯上主人的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.08,0:08:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不能让他们得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.48,0:08:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.60,0:08:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击开始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.09,0:08:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.78,0:08:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.54,0:08:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春 小心些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.15,0:08:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在无限制空间里 痛觉是普通对战的两倍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.28,0:08:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小拓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.31,0:08:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春 快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.00,0:08:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.90,0:08:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差一点了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.03,0:09:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差一点就到坑洞的边缘了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.82,0:09:05.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能到那里 就能抱着学姐和仁子一口气…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.42,0:09:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无用的挣扎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.58,0:09:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚人的旋转木马
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.60,0:09:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(424,430)}<Siuy Go-Round>
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.81,0:09:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.48,0:09:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空间在旋转？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 只是看上去在旋转罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.55,0:09:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭上眼睛 快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.05,0:09:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.79,0:09:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小拓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.77,0:09:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的 小春
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.90,0:09:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我欠你的 不会这么容易就能还清
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.12,0:09:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你根本没有欠我什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.30,0:09:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我说几次你才能明白啊 小拓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.50,0:09:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小拓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.93,0:09:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说你只会用脑的那句话我收回 蓝色之桩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.91,0:09:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(609,430)}<Cyan Pile>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.17,0:10:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有30秒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.79,0:10:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再过30秒 声波的必杀技就会失效了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.77,0:10:06.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.06,0:10:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来听说你有点本事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.22,0:10:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来只是靠给人当肉盾混饭的啊 蓝色之桩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.23,0:10:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(620,430)}<Cyan Pile>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.80,0:10:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你死之前给我记清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.81,0:10:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干掉你的人就是本大爷撒克逊人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.82,0:10:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(565,430)}<Saxon>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.51,0:10:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你这种笨蛋的名字…不感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.53,0:10:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷霆战枪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.54,0:10:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(424,430)}<Lightning Cyan Spike>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.12,0:10:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小拓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.34,0:10:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 就交给你了 小春
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.42,0:10:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴雨钉刺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.44,0:10:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(424,430)}<Splash Stinger>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.88,0:10:53.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小拓 你果然是很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.07,0:10:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我引以为傲的挚友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.17,0:11:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小拓…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.70,0:11:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐 学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.52,0:11:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑雪姬学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.60,0:11:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你不站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.82,0:11:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的 白银之鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.83,0:11:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(472,430)}<Silver Crow>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.15,0:11:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在从这女人灵魂中输出到虚拟角色上的讯号
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.26,0:11:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都被零填满了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.46,0:11:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有斗志的超频连接者是无法操纵虚拟对战角色的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.42,0:11:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有力量直面自己内心的伤痛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.69,0:11:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会连站立都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.88,0:11:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brain Burst就是这样一个游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.44,0:11:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内心的伤痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.48,0:11:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快带着睡莲跑吧 白银之鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.48,0:11:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(380,430)}<Lotus>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.48,0:11:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(525,430)}<Silver Crow>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.62,0:11:52.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.86,0:11:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然蓝色之桩奋不顾身为我们争取到了时间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.86,0:11:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(272,430)}<Cyan Pile>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.19,0:11:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我还没有胆小到能在这个时候说跑就跑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.45,0:12:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.98,0:12:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不会跑的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.56,0:12:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要丢下同伴自己逃走呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.01,0:12:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.72,0:12:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真是个彻头彻尾的笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就随你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.72,0:12:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄之声波
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.72,0:12:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(424,430)}<Yellow Radio>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.21,0:12:17.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在的必杀技槽应该已经全空了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.57,0:12:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这回该我们反击了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.32,0:12:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别忘了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.65,0:12:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是被我打败了的话就会从这个世界消失
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.41,0:12:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 强化外装
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.49,0:12:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思了 白银之鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.49,0:12:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(498,430)}<Silver Crow>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.29,0:12:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只要应付在我背后的近战型对手就行了 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.35,0:12:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我被他们打败了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.02,0:12:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就带着睡莲飞走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.02,0:12:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(452,430)}<Lotus>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.03,0:12:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:12:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们担心什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.81,0:12:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只不过是个固定炮台
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.27,0:13:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧贴着它打的话 它也就像铁块一样毫无还手之力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.07,0:13:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没必要害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.37,0:13:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧 小的们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.89,0:13:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的对手可是红之王
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.04,0:13:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会让你们印象深刻的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.88,0:13:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.60,0:13:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.17,0:13:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充数的就不要在这里碍事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.18,0:13:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,磁力波
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.18,0:13:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(424,430)}<Maganetron Wave>
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.47,0:13:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金属很容易被磁铁吸上的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.03,0:14:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 我的必杀技只能持续13秒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.24,0:14:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钻透你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.41,0:14:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到要和金属系中最难应付的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.77,0:14:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打击型对手进行近身战的情况时
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.83,0:14:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好要躲过对方的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.57,0:14:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用对方的力道反击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.27,0:14:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凭你的反应速度 这个作战策略是可行的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.49,0:14:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你平时一副无能的样子 干得还不赖嘛 白银之鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.49,0:14:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(667,430)}<Silver Crow>
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.89,0:14:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢夸奖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.91,0:15:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干扰波
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.95,0:15:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去找出来 乌鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.95,0:15:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(498,430)}<Crow>
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.97,0:15:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是他手下某个黄色家伙的招数
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.39,0:15:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.61,0:15:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电击理疗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.61,0:15:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(424,430)}<Electric Therapy>
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.36,0:15:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我们把红之王给扒光了之前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.50,0:15:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就在那睡会儿吧 小子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.04,0:15:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.13,0:15:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是多么狼狈多么难看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.54,0:15:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就没有半点王的威严
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.27,0:15:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到底也就是红色的暴发户和黑色的叛徒罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.51,0:15:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞定 红之王也只不过是这等货色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.89,0:15:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个 把她的铁皮全剥了 从里面拖出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.52,0:16:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐…学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.57,0:16:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能容忍这种情形吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.91,0:16:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种完结的方式是你愿意看到的吗 黑之王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.50,0:16:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你来说加速是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.63,0:16:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brain Burst是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.25,0:16:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的所谓达到前无古人的Lv10的野心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.72,0:16:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道比对一个男人的回忆更加廉价吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.41,0:16:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要在那种地方睡到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.26,0:16:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是要斩破了所有的障碍 横扫千军万马
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.10,0:16:46.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算流尽最后一滴血也要实现你的野心不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.61,0:16:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑之睡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.61,0:16:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(424,430)}<Black Lotus>
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.95,0:17:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学…姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.14,0:17:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春雪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.50,0:17:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.56,0:17:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和骑士怎么被你说得像是恋人关系似的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.56,0:17:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(257,430)}<Rider>
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.11,0:17:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.47,0:17:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.21,0:17:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说过了吗 你是我的第一个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.99,0:17:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 别老趴在地上 试试单手插入地面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.41,0:17:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.05,0:17:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 是地面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.04,0:17:48.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来的自己能解决吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.96,0:17:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去照看一下那丫头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.14,0:17:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.79,0:18:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 擒拿系的技能对我来说大都无效
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.04,0:18:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我虽然和你们无冤无仇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.29,0:18:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但和我战斗的人必将尝到某个部位残缺的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.27,0:18:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且在这个比平时多两倍的区域里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.48,0:18:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要现在才叫喊着「不要啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.41,0:18:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啊 我现在还在充电啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.37,0:18:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼才等你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.45,0:18:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.36,0:18:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.78,0:18:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么到现在才出来搅局
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.45,0:18:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是来妨碍我的吗 黑之睡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.44,0:18:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(539,430)}<Black Lotus>
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.19,0:18:51.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经忘了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.87,0:18:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘了你背叛我们 把朋友的头砍下了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.44,0:18:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他现在在哪里做着什么事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.97,0:19:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他会不会想起自己再也回不到加速世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.93,0:19:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和让他变成这样的那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.52,0:19:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我的话 是绝对不会忘记的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.68,0:19:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是平常的对战也就罢了 没想到居然是偷袭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.62,0:19:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.61,0:19:20.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有一点误会了 黄之声波
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.60,0:19:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(526,430)}<Yellow Radio>
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.58,0:19:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.55,0:19:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.95,0:19:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的首级和红之骑士的分量对我来说一样重
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.94,0:19:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(355,430)}<Red Rider>
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.75,0:19:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 再告诉你一件事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.07,0:19:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢 从第一次见到你开始
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.79,0:19:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就超级讨厌你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.32,0:19:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腥雨 剩下的外装再充电完毕了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.33,0:19:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(255,430)}<Rain>
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.48,0:19:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌鸦 掩护她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.46,0:19:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(379,430)}<Crow>
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.67,0:19:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.83,0:19:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我再休息一下好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.65,0:19:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌鸦 干扰电波的来源在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.63,0:19:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(281,430)}<Crow>
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.27,0:19:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.09,0:20:07.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经和那时候…不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.98,0:20:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.41,0:20:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.15,0:20:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.15,0:20:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(424,430)}<Lotus>
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.82,0:20:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快 这就是Lv9之间的战斗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.37,0:21:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好看着吧 加速世界开始以来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.43,0:21:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是首次Lv9之间的正面恶斗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.11,0:21:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.19,0:21:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人的必杀技槽差不多满了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.92,0:21:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在才开始亮真家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.97,0:21:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡莲的必杀技大概会是直接攻击系的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.98,0:21:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(230,430)}<Lotus>
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.81,0:21:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相反声波应该是幻觉系的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.81,0:21:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(353,430)}<Radio>
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.57,0:21:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在声波的必杀技打出来之前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.57,0:21:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(312,430)}<Radio>
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.07,0:21:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡莲的致命一击到底能不能命中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.07,0:21:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(258,430)}<Lotus>
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.66,0:21:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是决胜点了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.37,0:21:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宣告·贯通致死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.39,0:21:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(424,430)}<Death By Piercing>
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.50,0:21:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无意义的命运之轮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.51,0:21:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(424,430)}<Feudal Fortune Wheel>
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.02,0:23:40.86,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(675,396)}Absolution ; 宽恕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.82,0:23:36.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}下回 Absolution 宽恕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.63,0:23:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}在决战的时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.34,0:23:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}理当被宽恕的 能是由爱而生的罪么
